# IntelliQA Design System

## Tech Stack

- **React 18** + **Vite** (module bundler)
- **Ant Design v4** (`antd@^4.24.10`) — tables, modals, dropdowns, menus, selects, inputs
- **MUI 5** (`@mui/material`, `@mui/joy` beta, `@mui/x-*`) — buttons, cards, dialogs, typography, data-grid, charts
- **Emotion** (`@emotion/react`, `@emotion/styled`) — CSS-in-JS (required by MUI)
- **Tailwind CSS 3** — utility classes (`corePlugins.preflight: false` to avoid resetting Ant/MUI)
- **Sass** — available for SCSS if needed
- **No styled-components** — use Emotion or MUI `sx` prop

