## Glass Morphism (Frosted Glass Pattern)

Used in Header, GlassButton, popovers, sidebar, and minimap.

```
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72–0.95)
backdropFilter: blur(10px–20px) saturate(180%)
border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18–0.3)
borderRadius: 10px–16px
boxShadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.08)
```

### Header Glass Bar
```
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72)
backdropFilter: blur(10px) saturate(180%)
borderBottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)
boxShadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.08)
padding: py-[6px] px-[24px]
z-index: 100
```

### Frosted Popover Panel
```
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)
backdropFilter: blur(20px)
borderRadius: 16px
border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)
boxShadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)
```

## Transitions & Animations

### Standard Easings

| Name | Value | Usage |
|------|-------|-------|
| Default | `0.3s ease-in-out` | Input focus, card hover |
| Apple | `0.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)` | Buttons, search, sidebar |
| Fast | `0.18s` | Login button transform |

### Keyframe Animations (defined in `intelli-qa.css`)

`cardEntrance`, `floatIcon`, `shimmer`, `borderGlow`, `pulseGlow`, `fadeIn`, `slideDown`, `slideInFromLeft`, `slideInFromRight`, `expandCard`, `collapseToMini`, `connectorGrow`, `subCardAppear`, `backButtonAppear`

### Tailwind Animation

| Name | Keyframe | Duration |
|------|----------|----------|
| `pulse-dots` | opacity 0 → 1 → 0 | 1s cubic-bezier |
| `spin` | rotate 360deg | default spin |

## Component Patterns

### Buttons

**3 button systems exist — use the right one for the context:**

1. **`GlassButton`** (`src/pages/intelli-qa/components/GlassButton.jsx`)
   - Apple-inspired glassmorphic buttons
   - Props: `type="primary|secondary"`, `variant="glassmorphic|solid|outlined|text"`, `size="small|medium|large"`
   - Border-radius: 10px, letter-spacing: 0.5px, textTransform: none
   - Small: 28px height, Medium: 36px, Large: 44px

2. **`MuiButton` (IntelliQA)** (`src/pages/intelli-qa/components/MuiButton.jsx`)
   - 5 variants: `primary` (#043365), `secondary` (outlined #043365), `text`, `danger` (#D32F2F), `success` (#388E3C)
   - Height: 40px, minWidth: 110px, textTransform: capitalize

3. **`MuiButton` (Global)** (`src/components/MuiButton.jsx`)
   - Simple: only `primary` (contained #043365) or outlined
   - Use for non-IntelliQA pages

### Cards

- **`Card`** (`src/components/Card.jsx`) — Shadcn-style compound: `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, `CardDescription`, `CardContent`, `CardFooter`
  - border-radius: 8px, shadow: `0px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)`, border: 1px solid divider
- **`CustomCard`** (`src/components/CustomCard.jsx`) — Dashboard stat card with icon, title, value, subValue
  - border-radius: 8px, shadow: `0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`
- **IntelliQA cards** — Glass-style with gradient borders, shimmer `::after`, pulseGlow animation, hover gradients

### Modals / Dialogs

**Pattern A — MUI Modal (light overlay):**
```
backdrop: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04–0.25)
content: absolute centered, bgcolor: background.paper, borderRadius: 1, p: 3
width: ~1100px, height: ~85vh
```

**Pattern B — MUI Dialog:**
```
maxWidth: "sm", fullWidth: true
PaperProps: { borderRadius: "12px", boxShadow: "0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)" }
```

### Text Fields

- Standard: border `1.5px solid #d1d5db`, borderRadius `8px`, focus: `#1976d2` with `0 0 0 3px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.1)` ring
- Search: borderRadius `10px`, bg `rgba(142, 142, 147, 0.08)`, focus: Apple blue `#007AFF` with `0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)` ring
- Placeholder: 12.8px, weight 400, color `#8E8E93`

### Chips / Tags

- fontSize: 11px, bg: `rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)`, color: `#007AFF`
- border: `0.5px solid rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.2)`, borderRadius: 2 (MUI = 8px)
- shadow: `0 1px 2px rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1)`

### Tabs

- textTransform: none, fontSize: 0.875rem, fontWeight: 500
- Selected: color `#007AFF`, fontWeight 600
- Hover: bg `rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.05)`

### Accordions

- bg: `#fafbfc`, no border, borderRadius: 2, shadow: `0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04)`
- Hover shadow: `0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)`

## Layout Structure

### App Shell

```
LayoutMain: Box with bg #f5f5f7, height 100vh, overflow hidden
├── Header: fixed glass bar (z-100, py-6px px-24px)
└── Content area: height calc(100vh - 45px), marginTop 45px
    └── <Outlet /> (React Router)
```

### Sidebar

- Background: `#FAFAFA`, border-right: `1px solid #CDD6E0`
- Item height: 40px, collapsed width: 50/80px, expanded: 200/250px
- Active: bg `#E2E2E2`, text `#043365`, weight 600, left accent via `activeMenu.svg`

