## Key Design Tokens File

The richest token source is `src/pages/intelli-qa/ui-testing-2/test-case/themeStyles.js`. Import and use it:

```jsx
import { themeStyles } from "../path/to/themeStyles";

// Colors
themeStyles.colors.primary        // #0B1941
themeStyles.colors.appleBlue      // #007AFF
themeStyles.colors.background     // #f5f5f7

// Component sx props
sx={themeStyles.components.textField}
sx={themeStyles.components.accordion}
sx={themeStyles.components.chip}
sx={themeStyles.components.card}
sx={themeStyles.components.tab}

// Typography
{...themeStyles.typography.h1}
{...themeStyles.typography.h2}
```

